00:00:07,261 --> 00:00:08,978
Moon's up high, shining wide. 明月光，夜夜亮

13
00:00:08,978 --> 00:00:11,435
Counting sheep on my bed. 让我来看看：有谁睡得不香？

14
00:00:11,435 --> 00:00:14,371
Who's still awake? Tossing and turning? 把月光拉长，盖在你身上

15
00:00:14,371 --> 00:00:16,426
Little lamb, wool so white. 小羊羔，白又绵

16
00:00:16,426 --> 00:00:18,859
Why're you hiding from the rest? 为什么你和它们不一样？

17
00:00:18,859 --> 00:00:22,227
Glow in the dark, come when the sun sets 尾巴亮亮，让我惊喜异常

18
00:00:22,227 --> 00:00:26,396
Ayayayaya Ayayayayayaya 啊呀呀呀呀呀呀 啊呀呀呀呀呀呀呀

19
00:00:26,396 --> 00:00:29,586
I ring my bell, I ring my bell 摇摇铃铛，摇摇铃铛

20
00:00:29,586 --> 00:00:33,539
Meadow grass swaying slow. Gentle green with hints of gold. 青草长，风轻扬

21
00:00:33,539 --> 00:00:36,530
The twilight paints the end of summer 落日涂抹夏日终章

22
00:00:36,530 --> 00:00:38,658
Electric sheep, do you dream, 小羊羔，听我唱：

23
00:00:38,658 --> 00:00:41,067
of machines in your sleep? 你可也曾坠入梦乡？

24
00:00:41,067 --> 00:00:44,651
Or do you dream of running far and free 也在寻找，遥远的彼方

25
00:00:44,651 --> 00:00:48,515
Ayayayaya Ayayayayayaya 啊呀呀呀呀呀呀 啊呀呀呀呀呀呀呀

26
00:00:48,515 --> 00:00:51,954
I ring my bell, I ring my bell 摇摇铃铛，摇摇铃铛

27
00:00:51,954 --> 00:00:55,915
Ayayayaya Ayayayayayaya 啊呀呀呀呀呀呀 啊呀呀呀呀呀呀呀

28
00:00:55,915 --> 00:00:58,859
I ring my bell, I ring my bell 摇摇铃铛，摇摇铃铛

29
00:00:58,859 --> 00:01:03,203
Oh~DAMIDAMIDAMIO~Sunlight'll tell me where to go 哒咪哒咪哒咪哟~跟随日光

30
00:01:03,203 --> 00:01:06,563
We laugh and run, all night long 追逐白昼，让此刻停留

31
00:01:06,563 --> 00:01:10,566
DAMIDAMIDAMIO~ River guides the way we roam 哒咪哒咪哒咪哟~沿着河流

32
00:01:10,566 --> 00:01:14,813
When the night is gone, journey will carry on 夜色消散，明日继续新的旅途

33
00:01:14,813 --> 00:01:17,915
To the secret untold, to the wonder we hold 向着未言之秘，向着奇思妙想

34
00:01:17,915 --> 00:01:21,355
Running out the woods we know, little sheep we tip tap toe 奔出熟悉的森林，像小羊一般踮步起舞

35
00:01:21,355 --> 00:01:25,132
I wandered high and low, now I don't walk alone 四处旅行，直到找到一位朋友

36
00:01:25,132 --> 00:01:28,676
Together on we go 于是我们一同前行

37
00:01:28,676 --> 00:01:32,509
Wuu 呜

38
00:01:32,509 --> 00:01:36,052
Let's find a way out 一同前行

39
00:01:36,052 --> 00:01:37,644
Moon's up high, shining wide. 明月光，夜夜亮

40
00:01:37,644 --> 00:01:40,069
Set my heart upon a quest 我依然在旅途上

41
00:01:40,069 --> 00:01:43,347
I'm by myself, but far from lonely 请别在意，并不孤单彷徨

42
00:01:43,347 --> 00:01:44,996
Little lamb, wool so white. 小羊羔，白又绵

43
00:01:44,996 --> 00:01:47,581
Why're you running on your own? 其实我和你也一样

44
00:01:47,581 --> 00:01:51,405
I'm just like you, searching for where I belong. 漂泊的孩子想回到梦乡

45
00:01:51,405 --> 00:01:54,924
Ayayayaya Ayayayayayaya 啊呀呀呀呀呀呀 啊呀呀呀呀呀呀呀

46
00:01:54,924 --> 00:01:58,522
Wuu 呜

47
00:01:58,522 --> 00:02:00,177
Round and around, around we go~ 转呀转呀，一路向前；

48
00:02:00,177 --> 00:02:02,353
To the end I'll keep you close 伴你身边，直至终点

49
00:02:02,353 --> 00:02:05,778
I'll follow you and be your shadow 我像影子一样追随你

50
00:02:05,778 --> 00:02:07,656
Round n round, around we go. 转呀转呀，一路向前；

51
00:02:07,656 --> 00:02:09,745
Count the stars, then off you go 数着星星，你便不见

52
00:02:09,745 --> 00:02:15,848
If I catch you, promise don't hide again~ again~ 如果我抓住你了，请答应我：不要再藏起来了

53
00:02:15,848 --> 00:02:21,650
I ring my bell, I ring my bell 摇摇铃铛，摇摇铃铛

54
00:02:21,650 --> 00:02:25,354
DAMIDAMIDAMIO~ Sing the song we used to know 哒咪哒咪哒咪哟~唱起我们熟悉的歌

55
00:02:25,354 --> 00:02:28,828
We ride the winds, into the wild 乘风而行，奔向旷野

56
00:02:28,828 --> 00:02:32,649
DAMIDAMIDAMIO~ sing so loud the sky will know 哒咪哒咪哒咪哟~只要高声歌唱，天空也能听到

57
00:02:32,649 --> 00:02:36,784
We laugh we run, until the break of dawn 夜色消散，明日继续新的旅途

58
00:02:36,784 --> 00:02:40,193
To the secret untold, to the wonder we hold 向着未言之秘，向着奇思妙想

59
00:02:40,193 --> 00:02:43,746
Running out the woods we know, little sheep we tip tap toe 奔出熟悉的森林，像小羊一般踮步起舞

60
00:02:43,746 --> 00:02:47,258
I wandered high and low, now I don't walk alone 四处旅行，直到找到一位朋友

61
00:02:47,258 --> 00:02:51,314
Together on we go 于是我们一同前行

62
00:02:51,314 --> 00:02:54,314
The stars will take me home 星辰终将引我归家